<dependency>
    <groupId>io.quarkus</groupId>
    <artifactId>quarkus-undertow</artifactId>
</dependency>
```
Additionally, you may need to update the imports in your file to reflect the changes. Specifically, you will need to import `jakarta.enterprise.context.SessionScoped` instead of `jakarta.ejb.Stateful`.
